events.description:
7:00 - 7:30 Networking and food (Vegetarian options will be available)
7:30 - 8:30 Presentation

Vishal Kumar Resident Angular Expert at Delta Airlines will share his lessons learned on Lazy Loading from presentations at ngAtlanta and Manfred's full day Micro Apps workshop.

events.name: Adventures in Node and Nest
events.description:
Our story begins after you’ve created your Angular frontend: up until this point you’ve been using mock data and now you’re wondering “How in the world do I create the backend to power this application?” and “How can I leverage my existing Angular and TypeScript skills to do it”. In this talk we will go through setting up your perfect companion Backend. A Node server with Nest then extending the functionality to be ready for production.

Pizza, Wings and Soda will be provided
events.how_to_find_us: 6th floor. Call 937.594.5738 if you're locked out.

events.name: Intro to Flutter
events.description:
Food and Beverages will be provided at 6:30 PM. Talk begins promptly at 7:00PM and is presented by Rob Quatela and Manny Diera.

Let’s dive into the power of Flutter to develop cross platform mobile applications. We will go over our expectations going into flutter (history, pros of the platform), what is Dart, Flutter architecture (what are widgets), setup and run an app (explain the Material App widget), our experience with Flutter so far (good and recommendations). Lastly, we will go over some good IDE extensions.

This will take place on the 6th floor in the Ultimate Software office. Please call[masked] or message Zack if you cannot get into the building.
